    "Html": "<p>yeah got it. thanks erni23</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>chartingprimitives belongs to&nbsp;</p>\r\n<pre style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:15px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:10px;padding-right:10px;padding-bottom:35px;padding-left:10px;vertical-align:baseline;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-color:#f5f5f5;font-family:Consolas, 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;display:block;font-weight:normal;line-height:1.2em;min-height:35px;overflow-y:auto;overflow-x:scroll;white-space:pre;color:#494949;width:788px;font-size:0.75em;background-position:initial initial;background-repeat:initial initial;border:1px solid #dadada\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-color:transparent;color:#0000ff;background-position:initial initial;background-repeat:initial initial;padding:0px;margin:0px;border:0px initial initial\">&quot;clr-namespace:System.Windows.Controls.DataVisualization.Charting.Primitives;assembly=System.Windows.Controls.DataVisualization.Toolkit&quot;</span></pre>",
